abilities (PWD).Accordingly, applicant must be a regular student at any school, college or polytechnic college in MP.Students having Orthopedic disability must have secured at least 60% marks in their previous class.Furthermore students having disability other than orthopedic must have secured at-least 50% marks in the previous class.This scheme is for the welfare of the disabled persons and to provide them assistance for completion of their studies. Accordingly, the laptops will get distributed on 10 May 2018. For this reason, identification of candidates will get done till 30 January 2018.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}